Package javax.xml.crypto

Interface AlgorithmMethod

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    CanonicalizationMethod, DigestMethod, SignatureMethod, Transform
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    ApacheCanonicalizer, ApacheTransform, DOMBase64Transform, DOMCanonicalizationMethod, DOMCanonicalXMLC14N11Method, DOMCanonicalXMLC14NMethod, DOMDigestMethod, DOMEnvelopedTransform, DOMExcC14NMethod, DOMHMACSignatureMethod, DOMSignatureMethod, DOMTransform, DOMXPathFilter2Transform, DOMXPathTransform, DOMXSLTTransform, TransformService

    public interface AlgorithmMethod
    An abstract representation of an algorithm defined in the XML Security specifications. Subclasses represent specific types of XML security algorithms, such as a Transform.
    Since:
    1.6
